{"id":4465,"date":"2014-09-05T12:42:48","date_gmt":"2014-09-05T17:42:48","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/?page_id=4465"},"modified":"2020-03-19T08:45:23","modified_gmt":"2020-03-19T13:45:23","slug":"got-cpap","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/got-cpap","title":{"rendered":"Why do I feel exhausted in the morning?"},"content":{"rendered":"<ul>\n<li>Still tired in the morning? Always want &#8220;just one more hour?&#8221;<\/li>\n<li>Does your &#8220;Significant Other&#8221; say you snore like a walrus and stop breathing?<\/li>\n<li>Do you sometimes wake up gasping for air?<\/li>\n<li>Can&#8217;t stay asleep?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>You may have Sleep Apnea.<\/p>\n<p>Sleep apnea makes your sleep ineffective. No amount of bad sleep will make you feel rested.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/index.php\/epworth-sleepiness-test\">Take the Epworth Sleepiness Test<\/a> for free and see if you&#8217;re sleepier than you should to be!<\/p>\n<p>I did! It turned out that I had Obstructive Sleep Apnea, I got treated and now I wake up every morning read for the world!<br \/>\nNow when I go to sleep, I wake up feeling good!<\/p>\n<p>I wish I&#8217;d done it decades ago, since I had wasted literally decades feeling tired all the time.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure style=\"width: 630px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"padding: 4px; background-color: white; border: medium gray groove;\" title=\"Image used with permission of creator: reddit.com user &quot;BlorfMonger&quot;\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/cpap_comic.jpg\" alt=\"Went to the doc about my snoring. He made me do a sleep study, and I was given a cpap machine. WTF, all I do is snore. I don't need to be hooked up in my bed like a dying old man. Oh well, might as well give it a try....ZZzzzzz . . . . .. (wakes up) OMG! I haven't slept in years!!\" width=\"640\" height=\"1200\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Got CPAP?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Still tired in the morning? Always want &#8220;just one more hour?&#8221; Does your &#8220;Significant Other&#8221; say you snore like a walrus and stop breathing? Do you sometimes wake up gasping for air? Can&#8217;t stay asleep? You may have Sleep Apnea. Sleep apnea makes your sleep ineffective. No amount of bad sleep will make you feel &#8230; <a title=\"Why do I feel exhausted in the morning?\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/got-cpap\" aria-label=\"Read more about Why do I feel exhausted in the morning?\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":28,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-4465","page","type-page","status-publish"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4465","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/28"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4465"}],"version-history":[{"count":34,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4465\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5807,"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/4465\/revisions\/5807"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.bupkis.org\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4465"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}